fields.name: Curious baby bird
fields.description: As I walked around by a river listening to bird songs in a forest south-east from the city of Norrköping, I saw this little fellow watching the horizon from it's tower.

fields.name: Coast town of Ålesund
fields.description: This awesome view is at the cost of around 500 stairs. Once at the top the beauty of this place grabs you and can't be forgotten. It's worth every step.

fields.name: Rhodope dawn
fields.description: The magic exists, and it starts with first light in the warm hug of Rhodope mountain. One look is enough to realise that this place is like a fantasy world that was lost.

fields.name: Covered path
fields.description: Walking this path looks and feels like it's taking you straith in a George R.R. Martin's novel world. But don't worry it's in the beautiful Omberg Ekopark.

fields.name: Stairs in the wood
fields.description: When I saw this place in front of me, I thought the next thing to expect is a group of hobbits may be, or a company of a man, an elf and a dwarf!

fields.name: Lake view
fields.description: The long and sunny summer days are perfect for taking a walk around the countless lakes and see the world in their calm waters.

fields.name: Peaks in the clouds
fields.description: The greatness of this peaks scratching the skies leav a feeling of how small we are in the face of nature's creations.

fields.name: Oldtimer in shape
fields.description: Annually in the small town of Finspång can be seen a gathering of well preserve classic american cars and enjoy an atmosphere from decades ago.

fields.name: Urban paths
fields.description: Making your way in the tide but cosy streets of sunny San Sebastian can be a real pleasure. All you see is fine architecture in many colors.

fields.name: Sunrise in motion
fields.description: A beautiful sunrise catched from the cosy front passenger seat at the start of a long-awaited roadtrip always fill the mind with excitement.
